graph TD
    Start(PluginWatcherService Start) -->|Every 60s| Scan[Scan /plugins directory]
    Scan --> Compute[Compute SHA256 Hashes]
    Compute --> Check{Change Detected?}

    Check -- No --> Wait[Wait next cycle]
    Wait --> Scan

    Check -- Yes --> Type{Change Type}

    Type -- New JAR --> Copy[Copy to Temp Directory]
    Copy --> Load[Load Plugin]
    Load --> Register[Register Commands/Listeners]

    Type -- Hash Changed --> Status{Is Plugin Enabled?}
    Status -- No --> UpdateNow[Apply Update Immediately]
    UpdateNow --> Reload[Reload Plugin]

    Status -- Yes --> Queue[Queue Update]
    Queue --> Warn[Warn Admins every 1 min]
    Warn --> Action{Admin Action?}
    Action -- Disable --> UpdateNow
    Action -- Restart --> UpdateNow
    Action -- None --> Warn

    Type -- JAR Removed --> Unload[Unload Plugin]
    Unload --> Cleanup[Cleanup Temp Files]

    style Start fill:#afa,stroke:#333
    style Warn fill:#ffa,stroke:#333
    style UpdateNow fill:#aff,stroke:#333
